sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant WS as Workspace CLI
    participant PL as Platform
    participant PS as Proxy Supervisor
    participant CI as CI/CD Service
    participant GV as Gvisor Service
    participant MCP as MCP Server

    %% Development Phase
    Dev->>WS: Define models, tools, orchestrators
    Dev->>WS: Configure environment (dev/staging/prod)
    
    %% Packaging Phase
    WS->>WS: Generate application.config.json
    WS->>WS: Create KAR archive
    WS->>WS: Validate dependencies
    
    %% Deployment Phase
    WS->>PL: Call /deploy (upload config + archive)
    PL->>PL: Validate configuration
    PL->>PL: Store archive + metadata
    PL->>CI: Trigger deployment
    CI->>GV: Provision container
    GV->>MCP: Launch server with archive
    MCP->>MCP: Bootstrap environment
    MCP->>MCP: Install dependencies
    MCP->>MCP: Register tools & orchestrators
    MCP->>PL: Report ready/healthy
    
    %% Runtime Phase
    Note over PL,PS: For each runtime request
    PL->>PS: Forward event payload
    PS->>MCP: MCP Client: Connect
    PS->>MCP: MCP Client: Discover tools
    PS->>MCP: MCP Client: Send request
    MCP->>MCP: Process request
    MCP->>MCP: Execute tools/orchestrators
    MCP->>PS: Stream response chunks
    PS->>PL: Aggregate response
    
    %% Monitoring Phase
    Note over PL,GV: Continuous monitoring
    GV->>PL: Health status
    PL->>PL: Log monitoring data
    
    %% Undeployment Phase
    WS->>PL: Call /undeploy
    PL->>GV: Trigger container cleanup
    GV->>MCP: Stop server
    GV->>PL: Report cleanup complete
